  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/0fd7b216b93f9a1c7a6298c9df7e1c23.avif?t=1765063642\" width=500 height=309 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"Escape from the Cursed Convent\"</strong> is a narrative adventure game set in a medieval convent and it is a non official fan derivative work of the manga \"Hengoku no Schwester.\"  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/c05948ac18a7661e9959633788a12431.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/fe64df21fc16bd02c12e635e567d952a.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Step into the 16th-century Holy Roman Empire through the eyes of Adeline, a young peasant girl whose mother is falsely accused of witchcraft. Adeline is sent to the Claustrum Convent for \"re-education\" where she faces a living hell of torment and executions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Over the course of 5 to 8 hours, explore the convent’s dark world featuring subtle elements of gore and yuri. Determined to escape, Adeline and her friend Helena embark on a daring journey driven by themes of saintliness, freedom, and faith.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/32551b96ffbb96c6510d671242b09376.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/67fe02a0fedf2627d614fabeced21f5e.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Step into a mesmerizing pixel art world rich with authentic medieval religious details. Explore the beautifully crafted convent accompanied by period-specific music and a cast of intriguing characters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/c07113a6811e5cdebc65aade2a37b176.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/4280518c5c45fd520e0520e2510663fb.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Embark on an adventure spanning 5 to 8 hours where your choices influence the narrative. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Experience multiple endings and side stories as you navigate the convent's mysteries. Form deep, perhaps unexpected connections with your companions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/f008ecf1706286e7e75f555d1022dfc3.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/208a01d07d83ef8c009d2efe6286e01b.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Enhance your journey with a variety of mini-games. Engage in Quick Time Events, test your skills in hunting, perfect your cooking, and discover many more activities as you explore the world with your protagonists.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/0fd7b216b93f9a1c7a6298c9df7e1c23.avif?t=1765063642\" width=500 height=309 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"Escape from the Cursed Convent\"</strong> is a narrative adventure game set in a medieval convent and it is a non official fan derivative work of the manga \"Hengoku no Schwester.\"  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/c05948ac18a7661e9959633788a12431.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/fe64df21fc16bd02c12e635e567d952a.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Step into the 16th-century Holy Roman Empire through the eyes of Adeline, a young peasant girl whose mother is falsely accused of witchcraft. Adeline is sent to the Claustrum Convent for \"re-education\" where she faces a living hell of torment and executions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Over the course of 5 to 8 hours, explore the convent’s dark world featuring subtle elements of gore and yuri. Determined to escape, Adeline and her friend Helena embark on a daring journey driven by themes of saintliness, freedom, and faith.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/32551b96ffbb96c6510d671242b09376.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/67fe02a0fedf2627d614fabeced21f5e.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Step into a mesmerizing pixel art world rich with authentic medieval religious details. Explore the beautifully crafted convent accompanied by period-specific music and a cast of intriguing characters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/c07113a6811e5cdebc65aade2a37b176.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/4280518c5c45fd520e0520e2510663fb.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Embark on an adventure spanning 5 to 8 hours where your choices influence the narrative. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Experience multiple endings and side stories as you navigate the convent's mysteries. Form deep, perhaps unexpected connections with your companions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/f008ecf1706286e7e75f555d1022dfc3.webp?t=1765063642\" width=598 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142740/extras/208a01d07d83ef8c009d2efe6286e01b.avif?t=1765063642\" width=600 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Enhance your journey with a variety of mini-games. Engage in Quick Time Events, test your skills in hunting, perfect your cooking, and discover many more activities as you explore the world with your protagonists.</p>",
